q("mid247","mid2",C3,"An asthmatic patient given a non-selective β agonist to relieve bronchoconstriction — what adverse effect is expected?",["Tachycardia","Bradycardia","Hypotension","Bronchoconstriction"],0,"Non-selective β agonist → β1 stimulation → tachycardia and palpitations (while β2 provides the desired bronchodilation). Selective β2 agonists (salbutamol/albuterol) preferred in asthma."),
